269
00:23:01,200 --> 00:23:05,190
It turns out that the big fire back then
was not an accident.

270
00:23:07,210 --> 00:23:09,200
Mother set it.

271
00:23:10,160 --> 00:23:13,240
Your mother urged me to keep it from you.

272
00:23:13,240 --> 00:23:18,459
But I knew that one day you would find out.

273
00:23:21,528 --> 00:23:24,610
 

274
00:23:41,799 --> 00:23:46,659
Father, I want to discuss something with you.

275
00:23:46,659 --> 00:23:50,720
I plan to find the surviving family and relatives
of those who died from illness back then.

276
00:23:50,720 --> 00:23:54,259
If they need assistance,
I'll do my utmost to help them.

277
00:23:54,259 --> 00:23:59,720
I will also list the names of the deceased
to properly build tombs and monuments for them.

278
00:24:00,920 --> 00:24:02,759
Let me handle it.

279
00:24:02,759 --> 00:24:05,730
You were unaware back then,

280
00:24:06,670 --> 00:24:10,170
and as your father, I feel ashamed.

281
00:24:11,559 --> 00:24:18,980
You were trying to protect Mother and me.
You don't need to apologize to me.

282
00:24:19,519 --> 00:24:24,960
Moreover, I am also a member of the He family,
so I should make amends to those who suffered.

283
00:24:25,720 --> 00:24:31,440
I think it's what Mother would have wanted.

284
00:24:32,279 --> 00:24:37,419
Mu Dan, I know you are smart and capable.

285
00:24:38,039 --> 00:24:42,060
But as a woman,
you shouldn't worry about these things.

286
00:24:42,640 --> 00:24:47,340
There is much suffering in the world,
and it's hard for women to bear it.

287
00:24:47,340 --> 00:24:51,079
You ventured alone
into Chang'an and suffered a lot.

288
00:24:51,079 --> 00:24:55,860
Fortunately, you married into the Jiang family
and found a good husband.

289
00:24:56,440 --> 00:25:02,200
Although Jiang Chang Yang does not have
a good reputation, he is still of noble birth.

290
00:25:02,200 --> 00:25:06,440
He can ensure that you do not
suffer or get bullied.

291
00:25:06,440 --> 00:25:11,340
Now you need to look forward
and manage household affairs well.

292
00:25:11,340 --> 00:25:14,039
Serve your husband and ensure
the continuation of the lineage.

293
00:25:14,039 --> 00:25:19,659
Seek honor and favor.
Only then can you achieve lasting happiness.

294
00:25:21,480 --> 00:25:26,440
Father, I am talking about making amends with you.

295
00:25:26,440 --> 00:25:31,119
Yet you talk to me about how competing for favor
within the household can bring happiness.

296
00:25:31,119 --> 00:25:36,180
- You are a woman, and this is your destiny. 
 - Father,

297
00:25:36,180 --> 00:25:40,559
when I fled from the Liu Mansion
and returned home late at night,

298
00:25:40,559 --> 00:25:45,719
did you know why I didn't enter the house
and instead went straight to Chang'an?

299
00:25:45,719 --> 00:25:49,279
Because when the Liu family
came to look for me back then,

300
00:25:49,279 --> 00:25:54,599
I was nearby, and I overheard your conversation.

301
00:25:55,200 --> 00:25:59,979
You said yourself
a woman's only destination is marriage.

302
00:25:59,979 --> 00:26:03,979
If you found me, you would certainly
send me back to the Liu family.

303
00:26:03,979 --> 00:26:06,480
In your heart,

304
00:26:06,480 --> 00:26:09,140
marrying into the Liu family was my great honor,

305
00:26:09,140 --> 00:26:12,599
and leaving my husband was a disgrace to myself.

306
00:26:12,599 --> 00:26:17,959
I… I didn't know at the time
that the Liu family intended to take your life, I…

307
00:26:24,839 --> 00:26:31,359
Mu Dan, you are different now than before.

308
00:26:32,580 --> 00:26:34,259
How different?

309
00:26:34,259 --> 00:26:38,179
You are now Jiang Chang Yang's concubine.

310
00:26:38,179 --> 00:26:42,380
It was a mistake on my part back then.

311
00:26:42,380 --> 00:26:48,820
Now I hear that Jiang is very fond of you,
and that he doesn't have an official wife.

312
00:26:48,820 --> 00:26:54,480
You should work hard
and not repeat the mistake with the Liu family.

313
00:26:55,699 --> 00:26:57,510
Father,

314
00:26:59,140 --> 00:27:04,390
you have always loved and protected me.

315
00:27:04,979 --> 00:27:07,399
Yet meanwhile, you look down on me.

316
00:27:08,960 --> 00:27:16,419
When I escaped from the Liu family,
I faked my own death and changed my identity.

317
00:27:16,419 --> 00:27:22,019
I worked hard in business, just to avoid living a life confined to the house and depending on others.

318
00:27:22,019 --> 00:27:26,100
Mu Dan, it's not as simple as you think.

319
00:27:26,799 --> 00:27:31,699
You have no idea how difficult it is
to run a business and support a family,

320
00:27:31,699 --> 00:27:34,559
especially when you are a woman.

321
00:27:34,559 --> 00:27:37,839
You must know that your ability
to act and speak like this now

322
00:27:37,839 --> 00:27:40,499
is all because Jiang Chang Yang has your back.

323
00:27:40,499 --> 00:27:43,300
Do you really think this way?

324
00:27:43,300 --> 00:27:47,459
In your eyes, a woman can only rely on a man.

325
00:27:47,459 --> 00:27:51,779
At least he can make things
a bit easier for you, right?

326
00:27:59,000 --> 00:28:01,060
Maybe you see

327
00:28:02,150 --> 00:28:07,200
Mother as just a woman
who knows only gardening.

328
00:28:08,300 --> 00:28:14,659
But in my heart, she is the most
courageous and capable woman.

329
00:28:14,659 --> 00:28:17,540
 
Even in the most difficult times,

330
00:28:17,540 --> 00:28:22,979
she cared about the disaster victims
and made medicinal packets with peony bark.

331
00:28:22,979 --> 00:28:25,599
In the most painful times,

332
00:28:25,599 --> 00:28:32,240
she burned her beloved peony bushes
to refuse to be corrupted by the powerful.

333
00:28:32,979 --> 00:28:39,079
It was Mother who taught me that in this world,
women can have another way of life.

334
00:28:41,000 --> 00:28:45,660
And Father, I understand that back then,

335
00:28:45,660 --> 00:28:49,630
for the sake of this family, you had no choice but to set aside your dignity

336
00:28:49,630 --> 00:28:51,939
and make a deal with the powerful people.

337
00:28:52,659 --> 00:28:59,079
I can understand even more that you want
to pass on the family line for our ancestry,

338
00:29:00,019 --> 00:29:04,079
so you had to choose Man Er
and put your daughter second.

339
00:29:04,939 --> 00:29:07,540
But up to this day,

340
00:29:07,540 --> 00:29:12,939
you have never truly understood
what kind of women Mother and I are.

341
00:29:12,939 --> 00:29:18,100
What my heart desires is something
you cannot understand.

342
00:29:18,100 --> 00:29:24,419
Therefore, I cannot do what you ask of me.

343
00:29:24,419 --> 00:29:28,460
Mu Dan, why are you so willful?

344
00:29:28,460 --> 00:29:32,200
Everything I do is for your own good.

345
00:29:36,659 --> 00:29:39,459
As for how to establish oneself
in the world as a woman,

346
00:29:39,459 --> 00:29:42,780
I have already made up my mind.

347
00:29:44,119 --> 00:29:48,140
It's getting late. I should head back now.

348
00:29:48,140 --> 00:29:51,380
So that Auntie won't be unhappy.

349
00:29:51,380 --> 00:29:54,580
I thought you'd stay a few more days.

350
00:29:55,240 --> 00:29:59,459
No, there are still many things to do in Chang'an.

351
00:30:00,800 --> 00:30:02,490
Father,

352
00:30:03,580 --> 00:30:09,060
you are getting on in years.
You don't need to worry much about the pharmacy.

353
00:30:09,060 --> 00:30:15,459
I have already sent someone with money and silk.
They should arrive within two days.

354
00:30:15,459 --> 00:30:19,839
This money and silk should be enough
to help the He family start afresh.

355
00:30:20,599 --> 00:30:22,320
From now on,

356
00:30:22,320 --> 00:30:28,380
Father can live comfortably
in Luoyang with Man Er and Auntie.

357
00:30:49,620 --> 00:30:55,919
I will always remember
your kindness in raising me.

358
00:30:57,939 --> 00:31:03,019
As for my own matters, I will handle them myself.

359
00:31:03,019 --> 00:31:05,359
Please rest assured, Father.

360
00:31:20,540 --> 00:31:27,900
Mu Dan, why not eat before you go back?

361
00:31:45,759 --> 00:31:49,259
Father, I want to eat Hu cakes.

362
00:31:50,340 --> 00:31:53,759
Okay, I will make it for you.

363
00:32:02,799 --> 00:32:08,419
No, Father, please take care of yourself.

364
00:32:28,200 --> 00:32:31,279
Mr. Jiang, Ms. He has returned.

365
00:32:31,279 --> 00:32:36,380
So soon? I thought she would stay
in Luoyang for a few more days.

366
00:32:36,380 --> 00:32:39,060
Fu said that as soon as Ms. He returned
to the Fragrance Garden, she sent the guests away,

367
00:32:39,060 --> 00:32:43,380
closed the doors early
and was completely distraught.

368
00:32:46,599 --> 00:32:48,640
She knows everything.

369
00:33:01,000 --> 00:33:05,600
 I also hoped my parents
could have a pack of clouds. 

370
00:33:05,600 --> 00:33:09,739
 But even until they died kneeling
at the pharmacy's door, no one cared. 

371
00:33:10,519 --> 00:33:14,839
The people in the village
also collapsed one by one.

372
00:33:15,880 --> 00:33:18,799
The open space in the back hill
could no longer accommodate.

373
00:33:18,799 --> 00:33:23,380
Too many people died, too many.

374
00:33:23,380 --> 00:33:27,759
Mr. Wu said that the peony owner
turned a blind eye to death,

375
00:33:27,759 --> 00:33:30,939
so the peony bark she had
was no different from poison.

376
00:33:30,939 --> 00:33:35,340
The He family pharmacy is the murderous demon

377
00:33:35,340 --> 00:33:37,659
 and our enemy. 

378
00:34:16,300 --> 00:34:18,000
Mu Dan.

379
00:34:21,280 --> 00:34:23,719
When did you find out?

380
00:34:34,480 --> 00:34:41,380
I just learned about this from Mr. Wu
before you went to see him.

381
00:34:42,800 --> 00:34:48,140
During the flood four years ago,
he had never seen you.

382
00:34:48,140 --> 00:34:51,360
He didn't know you were the daughter
of Shopkeeper He of Luoyang.

383
00:34:53,099 --> 00:34:58,419
His acquaintance with you before
was out of appreciation for you.

384
00:35:00,860 --> 00:35:03,700
But he did harm your mother,

385
00:35:05,890 --> 00:35:08,360
so you have every right to hate him.

386
00:35:16,820 --> 00:35:18,820
Does it still hurt?

387
00:35:25,000 --> 00:35:31,740
I know you stopped me
from killing Mr. Wu for my sake.

388
00:35:33,719 --> 00:35:37,180
You feared I would learn
the brutal truth from four years ago.

389
00:35:39,320 --> 00:35:44,040
And you're even more afraid
that when I find out about the flood incident,

390
00:35:44,860 --> 00:35:50,419
I'll regret my previous impulsive actions.

391
00:35:53,199 --> 00:35:54,999
I'm sorry.

392
00:35:57,579 --> 00:36:02,740
There's no need for these words between us.

393
00:36:04,700 --> 00:36:11,879
But these words can never be heard
by Mother or those who died four years ago.

394
00:36:14,780 --> 00:36:17,660
As a pharmacist,

395
00:36:17,660 --> 00:36:23,539
Father couldn't protect Mother and me
if he didn't submit to those in power.

396
00:36:25,220 --> 00:36:27,930
As a beneficiary,

397
00:36:29,220 --> 00:36:32,160
I have no right to criticize him.

398
00:36:34,139 --> 00:36:38,939
But those common people
who died of illness did nothing wrong.

399
00:36:41,019 --> 00:36:45,880
I was determined to uncover the truth
and avenge my mother.

400
00:36:47,220 --> 00:36:49,870
But in the end,

401
00:36:50,820 --> 00:36:56,560
I found that there was
no one to hate and no revenge to seek.

402
00:36:58,340 --> 00:37:01,420
I always believed that by doing these things,

403
00:37:02,360 --> 00:37:06,550
I could bring beauty and fragrance to others.

404
00:37:07,199 --> 00:37:09,130
Little did I know

405
00:37:10,400 --> 00:37:12,920
there were so many others,

406
00:37:12,920 --> 00:37:18,059
struggling to survive, let alone enjoying flowers.

407
00:37:21,660 --> 00:37:25,959
Heaven and earth are unkind,
and the world is bleak.

408
00:37:26,539 --> 00:37:32,620
Suddenly, I don't know how to be
a good merchant anymore.

409
00:37:34,579 --> 00:37:37,530
Even if I became the top flower merchant,

410
00:37:38,940 --> 00:37:41,540
what is the point of it all?

411
00:37:54,059 --> 00:37:58,979
Mu Dan, since you started your business,

412
00:37:58,979 --> 00:38:03,900
you have never earned ill-gotten gains
or done anything against your conscience.

413
00:38:03,900 --> 00:38:06,119
You reopened the Fragrance Garden,

414
00:38:06,119 --> 00:38:10,220
giving those homeless women who had no one
something to depend on.

415
00:38:11,539 --> 00:38:14,459
How can that be pointless?

416
00:38:17,400 --> 00:38:24,619
I've trapped myself in this small space,
unable to see the true face of the world.

417
00:38:25,419 --> 00:38:29,740
What truly is the way of doing business?

418
00:38:31,180 --> 00:38:33,590
I can't figure it out anymore.

419
00:38:35,530 --> 00:38:37,910
I'm confused.

420
00:39:26,419 --> 00:39:28,220
Is there anything left?

421
00:39:28,220 --> 00:39:30,660
The accounts for this month have been settled.

422
00:39:30,660 --> 00:39:36,619
All the goods have been paid for,
except for the last order to be delivered.

423
00:39:37,440 --> 00:39:41,419
Fu, Chun, you will join me when the time comes.

424
00:39:48,260 --> 00:39:52,419
I have summarized
everyone's skills and work experience.

425
00:39:52,419 --> 00:39:55,099
Madam Tang, after I leave,

426
00:39:55,099 --> 00:39:59,300
 
please arrange everything properly on my behalf.

427
00:39:59,300 --> 00:40:02,740
Make sure that everyone
has a suitable position in the branch.

428
00:40:02,740 --> 00:40:04,660
When transferred to work in the shop,

429
00:40:04,660 --> 00:40:08,820
if everyone still wishes to live
in the Fragrance Garden, it is also fine.

430
00:40:08,820 --> 00:40:11,839
Mu Dan, what are you doing?

431
00:40:12,380 --> 00:40:18,479
After delivering this last order,
Fragrance Garden will temporarily close.

432
00:40:22,960 --> 00:40:27,860
The contracts for Huamanzhu and Qingshuzhai,
as well as the pawnshop receipts, are all inside.

433
00:40:27,860 --> 00:40:32,019
Ms. Sun, it will be left to you
for safekeeping in the future.

434
00:40:32,679 --> 00:40:37,700
In the future, with you managing
this shop, I am at ease.

435
00:40:37,700 --> 00:40:40,419
Huamanzhu and Fragrance Garden
are both famous throughout the capital.

436
00:40:40,419 --> 00:40:44,419
Are you willing to give up
all your efforts and achievements?

437
00:40:44,419 --> 00:40:48,039
Yes, Mu Dan, have you really thought this through?

438
00:40:48,939 --> 00:40:52,459
Through this incident, I have reflected a lot.

439
00:40:52,459 --> 00:40:56,320
The once-firm obsessions
and grand aspirations have all become vague.

440
00:40:56,320 --> 00:40:59,660
Even if I forcibly keep going,
it's still meaningless.

441
00:41:00,220 --> 00:41:04,820
I need to clear my thoughts
and figure out the true meaning

442
00:41:04,820 --> 00:41:07,800
of doing business.

